title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-17-2013 TUES
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-17-2013 TUES






Tuesday, December 17, 2013


David Horowitz Describes The Left

 
 

 - 9AM hour

1. New studies indicate multivitamins are of no value. 

2. Federal judge says NSA metadata mining violates the U.S. Constitution's 4th amendment. 

3. Majority of Colorado sherrifs refuse to enforce recently passed gun laws.




 - 10AM hour

Guest: David Horowitz, author of, 

"The Black Book of the American Left: The Collected Conservative Writings of David Horowitz."





 - 11AM hour

Mike provides a history of southern Democrats.
